Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
selectGroup(25.10)                                          selectGroup(25.10)

Name
       selectGroup - Selects a group

Syntax
        selectGroup

       [-help]

       <groupName>

       Selects a group. You can use this command after importing the design.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes the type and default
              information for each selectGroup parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man selectGroup

       <groupName>
              Specifies the name of the group.

              Data_type: string, required

Related Information
              * deselectGroup

              * Floorplanning the Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

